import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { ISlotListPlum } from '../slot-list-plum.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-slot-list-plum-detail', templateUrl: './slot-list-plum-detail.component.html', }) export class SlotListPlumDetailComponent implements OnInit { slotListPlum: ISlotListPlum | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ slotListPlum }) => { this.slotListPlum = slotListPlum; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
